ning statement is that the levels of youth unemployment at the moment across </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">Europe</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">, in my opinion, are unacceptably high.</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">I a</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">m encouraged to see that policymakers, at both </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">EU and national level, have realised that they have to act as a matter of urgency.</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">Personally</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">,</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> I am not sure that some of the measures proposed are sufficient to addre</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">ss the magnitude of the problem</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> but at least a start has been made. </span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:200%; margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">The Chairman:</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> An opening statement from you, Mr Mascherini?</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:200%; margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">Mr Mascherini</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">: </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">No. </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">I would like to thank the Committee for the invitation and I look forward to the questions.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:200%; m