 can send it to the Committee.</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> That was for </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">Austria</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:200%; margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">The other thing is </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">that the Eurofound study on the</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> Youth Guarantee shows that there are some critical factors for the success of the Youth Guarantee, one of which is capacity, Public Employment Services capacity, quality of advice and number of advisers.</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">There is a big discrepancy in the capacity of Public Employment Services across the EU</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">,</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> as you can imagine.</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> The Youth E</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">mployment </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">I</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">nitiative</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> is front</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">loaded for 2014 and 2015</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">. I do not know whether there</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> is enough space to develop the capacity in member states if it is not adequate.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:200%; margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">Also, in a number of member states t